    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RelationshipImpl
    public interface Relationship
extends ArchitectureElement, TechnologyConsumer
    A representation of the model object 'Relationship'. A relationship between two nodes. Relationships are contained by their source nodes and reference their targets using the target reference.

    The following features are supported:

    • Target
